    dc:creator "Dorchin, Netta; Freidberg, Amnon" ;
    dc:date "2008" ;
    dc:title "The Chenopodiaceae-feeding gall midges (Diptera: Cecidomyiidae) of the Na’aman salt marsh, Israel" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184989>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184990>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184986> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184989>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25 – 29. Careopalpis akko. 25. Head. 26. Apical flagellomeres. 27. Acropod 28. Female abdomen, lateral. 29. Ovipositor, lateral. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/184989/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184990>
    dc:description "FIGURES 30 – 35. Careopalpis akko. 30. Male terminalia, dorsal. 31. Gonostylus, dorsal (right), ventral (left). 32. Larva, ventral habitus. 33. Larva head. 34. Pupa, ventral. 35. Pupa, lateral. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/184990/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184986>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 10. Galls and infestation. 5. Baldratia salicorniae gall (arrow) in stem of Sarcocornia perennis. 6. A section through B. salicorniae gall, showing a larva. 7. Careopalpis akko gall (arrow) in leaf of Suaeda splendens. 8. Houardiella gracilis exuviae in dried stem joint of Arthrocnemum macrostachyum. 9 – 10. Stefaniella brevipalpis stem and leaf galls on Atriplex portulacoides." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/184986/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

